      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nCalling ldlm_flock_blocking_link() in ldlm_init_export() will cause FLock hashing stuff to be allocated for all types of exports when it is only required for mdts and not for all clients. I wonder if we need to do it there or better in ldlm_handle_enqueue0() ?",
